  "body_html": "<p data-start=\"31\" data-end=\"73\">Two vanilla perfumes, endless compliments.</p>\n<p data-start=\"75\" data-end=\"177\"><strong data-start=\"75\" data-end=\"85\">Sundae</strong> — our bestselling vanilla. Sweet, creamy, and deliciously gourmand with rich caramel notes.</p>\n<p data-start=\"179\" data-end=\"307\"><strong data-start=\"179\" data-end=\"197\">Salted Vanilla</strong> — a chic vanilla blend with salted caramel and roasted nuts, giving it a lighter, more addictive summer feel.</p>\n<p data-start=\"309\" data-end=\"424\">Wear them on their own or layer them together for the ultimate vanilla dream. Sweet, warm, salty, and irresistible.</p>\n<p data-start=\"426\" data-end=\"484\"><strong data-start=\"426\" data-end=\"446\">Bundle includes:</strong><br>• Sundae 50ml<br data-start=\"460\" data-end=\"463\">• Salted Vanilla 50ml</p>\n<p data-start=\"486\" data-end=\"531\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">The perfect duo for every vanilla lover. 🤍🍦</p>",
